# Keep Documentation Updated

When making changes to this repository, you MUST update the relevant documentation in `docs/` and root-level files. Documentation that falls out of sync is worse than no documentation.

## What Triggers a Docs Update

| Change | Files to Update |
|-----|----|
| Add/remove/rename an agent | `docs/pipeline-overview.md` (flow diagrams), `docs/adding-agents.md`, `docs/project-structure.md`, `README.md` (agent table), `CLAUDE.md` |
| Change pipeline flow or orchestrator logic | `docs/pipeline-overview.md`, `docs/ralph-loop.md` |
| Change prompt assembly or Ralph Loop mechanics | `docs/ralph-loop.md` |
| Add/remove MCP servers | `docs/mcp-integrations.md`, `README.md` (setup section) |
| Add/remove/rename source files or directories | `docs/project-structure.md` |
| Change environment variables | `.env.example`, `docs/project-structure.md` (file reference table) |
| Change dev container setup | `docs/project-structure.md` |
| Add/modify Cursor skills | `docs/project-structure.md` |
| Change context skill format or assembly | `docs/pipeline-overview.md`, `docs/project-structure.md`, `templates/context-skill.md` |
| Change PRD generation | `docs/pipeline-overview.md`, `docs/project-structure.md` |
| Change installation or CLI setup | `README.md` (installation section), `docs/prerequisites.md`, `scripts/install.sh` |
| Change Cargo dependencies | `Cargo.toml`, `docs/project-structure.md` (dependencies table) |
| Change CLI flags or subcommands | `src/cli.rs`, `docs/pipeline-overview.md` (CLI reference), `README.md` |

## Checklist

Before considering a change complete, verify:
- [ ] All Mermaid diagrams still reflect the actual system behavior
- [ ] The file reference table in `docs/project-structure.md` is accurate
- [ ] `README.md` matches the current setup and usage instructions
- [ ] `CLAUDE.md` matches the current project structure
- [ ] `Cargo.toml` dependencies match what `src/` actually imports
